@startuml ProcessPayment
title Process Payment Flow

actor "Cashier\nApp" as Cashier
participant "API\nGateway" as Gateway
participant "Payment\nService" as PS
participant "Order\nService" as OS
participant "Order Status\nService" as OSS
participant "ActiveMQ" as Queue
database "Payment DB" as PDB
database "Order DB" as ODB

Cashier -> Gateway: POST /orders/{orderId}/payments\n{method: "CREDIT_CARD", amount: 50}
activate Gateway
Gateway -> PS: Forward request
activate PS

PS -> OS: GET /orders/{orderId}
activate OS
OS -> ODB: Fetch order details
ODB --> OS: Order{items, totalPrice}
OS --> PS: Order data
deactivate OS

note over PS
  Calculate Total:
  - Fetch all items from order
  - Exclude CANCELLED items
  - Sum: 15.00 + 15.00 = 30.00
  - Request amount: 50.00
end note

PS -> OSS: GET /orders/{id}/items/{id}/status
activate OSS
OSS --> PS: Item statuses
deactivate OSS

PS -> PDB: CREATE Payment Record
activate PDB
note over PDB
  Payment fields:
  - id: UUID (NEW)
  - orderId: UUID
  - amount: 30.00
  - method: CREDIT_CARD
  - status: SUCCEEDED
  - createdAt: timestamp
  - transactionId: UUID
end note
PDB --> PS: Payment{id, orderId, amount, status}
deactivate PDB

PS -> Queue: PUBLISH PaymentSucceededEvent
activate Queue
Queue -> OSS: Async listener (payments topic)
OSS -> OSS: UPDATE Order.status = PAID
deactivate Queue

PS --> Gateway: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate PS
Gateway --> Cashier: Payment{id: UUID, amount: 30.00, status: SUCCEEDED}
deactivate Gateway
@enduml
